data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_14","content":"\r100  182k    0  182k    0     0   207k      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:--  207k\n16:<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Raise a glass at Dark Shepherd, The Star Brisbane. Explore a curated drinks menu featuring fine wines, crafted cocktails, and refreshing options designed to complement bold Mediterranean flavours.\"/>\n19:<meta itemprop=\"description\" content=\"Raise a glass at Dark Shepherd, The Star Brisbane. Explore a curated drinks menu featuring fine wines, crafted cocktails, and refreshing options designed to complement bold Mediterranean flavours.\"/>\n23:<meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Raise a glass at Dark Shepherd, The Star Brisbane. Explore a curated drinks menu featuring fine wines, crafted cocktails, and refreshing options designed to complement bold Mediterranean flavours.\"/>\n24:<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Raise a glass at Dark Shepherd, The Star Brisbane. Explore a curated drinks menu featuring fine wines, crafted cocktails, and refreshing options designed to complement bold Mediterranean flavours.\" />\n2224:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><div class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text-container\"><span class=\"sqsrte-scaled-text\"><h1 style=\"text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;\">THE BAR</h1></span></div></div>\n2747:  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">The bar at Dark Shepherd is where shadows stir and spirits rise. Signature cocktails crafted with precision offer a playful twist on timeless classics, while a 140-bottle wine list beckons connoisseurs and casual sippers alike. From robust reds to crisp whites, every bottle is handpicked to dance with the bold flavours of our menu. </p><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">Our extensive range of premium spirits and perfectly chilled Biers ensure no thirst goes unquenched. Whether you’re toasting the night away or savouring a quiet moment, the Dark Shepherd bar is a sophisticated escape where every sip is steeped in style and story.</p></div>\n3163:          <div class=\"menu-section-title\">SIGNATURE COCKTAILS</div>\n3179:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Botanic Bloom Spritz</div>\n3192:                  <div class=\"menu-item-option\">White Oat Strawberry & Apple   Sour Gin, Lemongrass syrup, Plum bitters, Sparkling wine & Soda.</div>\n3207:              <div class=\"menu-item-title\">Casanova</div>\n","isError":false}

