event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"I have enough to codify the brand: blackened ember base, warm stone surfaces, white logo usage, restrained amber accent, serif-led luxury copy, and photography as the main flourish. The section rhythm will be home hero, three destination cards for menu/functions/bar, provenance/menu highlights, events detail, then practical booking/contact."}

