id: 235
event: agent
data: {"type":"tool_result","toolUseId":"item_32","content":"<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Dark Shepherd · Mediterranean Restaurant at The Star Brisbane</title>\n  <style>\n    :root {\n      --bg:      oklch(12% 0.014 55);\n      --surface: oklch(18% 0.018 55);\n      --fg:      oklch(93% 0.018 78);\n      --muted:   oklch(70% 0.025 76);\n      --border:  oklch(34% 0.025 60);\n      --accent:  oklch(66% 0.12 55);\n\n      --accent-soft: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 14%, transparent);\n      --fg-soft:     color-mix(in oklch, var(--fg) 6%, transparent);\n\n      --font-display: 'Iowan Old Style', 'Charter', Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;\n      --font-body:    -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;\n      --font-mono:    ui-monospace, 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', Menlo, monospace;\n\n      --fs-h1: clamp(48px, 7vw, 104px);\n      --fs-h2: clamp(34px, 4.2vw, 58px);\n      --fs-h3: 22px;\n      --fs-lead: 19px;\n      --fs-body: 16px;\n      --fs-meta: 13px;\n\n      --gap-xs: 8px;\n      --gap-sm: 12px;\n      --gap-md: 20px;\n      --gap-lg: 32px;\n      --gap-xl: 56px;\n      --gap-2xl: 96px;\n      --container: 1180px;\n      --gutter: 32px;\n\n      --radius: 2px;\n      --radius-lg: 4px;\n    }\n\n    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }\n    html { -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; scroll-behavior: smooth; }\n    body {\n      margin: 0;\n      background: var(--bg);\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font-family: var(--font-body);\n      font-size: var(--fs-body);\n      line-height: 1.55;\n      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;\n      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n    }\n    img, svg { display: block; max-width: 100%; }\n    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }\n    button { font: inherit; cursor: pointer; }\n    p { text-wrap: pretty; }\n    h1, h2, h3, h4 { text-wrap: balance; }\n    .container { max-width: var(--container); margin-inline: auto; padding-inline: var(--gutter); }\n    .section { padding-block: clamp(56px, 9vw, var(--gap-2xl)); }\n    .section + .section { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }\n    .stack > * + * { margin-top: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .row-between { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .grid-2-1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    .grid-1-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: start; }\n    @media (max-width: 920px) {\n      .grid-2, .grid-3, .grid-4, .grid-2-1, .grid-1-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .topnav nav { display: none; }\n      .hero-plate { min-height: 520px; }\n      .menu-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n      .page-links { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n    }\n    .h1, h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h1); line-height: 0.96; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0; }\n    .h2, h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h2); line-height: 1.04; letter-spacing: -0.015em; margin: 0; }\n    .h3, h3 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--fs-h3); font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.22; letter-spacing: 0; margin: 0; }\n    .lead { font-size: var(--fs-lead); line-height: 1.55; color: var(--muted); max-width: 60ch; margin: 0; }\n    .eyebrow {\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 12px;\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      color: var(--accent);\n      margin: 0 0 var(--gap-md);\n    }\n    .meta { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--fs-meta); color: var(--muted); }\n    .num { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\n    .topnav {\n      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10;\n      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg) 88%, transparent);\n      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n    }\n    .topnav-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding-block: 14px; }\n    .topnav .logo { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 0.01em; }\n    .topnav .logo img { width: 116px; height: auto; }\n    .topnav nav { gap: var(--gap-lg); }\n    .topnav nav a { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.07em; }\n    .topnav nav a:hover { color: var(--fg); }\n    .pagefoot { padding-block: var(--gap-xl); color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .pagefoot .row-between { flex-wrap: wrap; gap: var(--gap-md); }\n    .btn {\n      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;\n      padding: 12px 22px;\n      border-radius: var(--radius);\n      border: 1px solid transparent;\n      font-size: 14px;\n      font-weight: 600;\n      letter-spacing: 0.07em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      transition: transform 0.05s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;\n    }\n    .btn:active { transform: translateY(1px); }\n    .btn-primary { background: var(--accent); color: var(--bg); border-color: var(--accent); }\n    .btn-primary:hover { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 88%, var(--fg)); }\n    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); border-color: var(--border); }\n    .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: var(--fg); }\n    .btn-ghost { background: transparent; color: var(--fg); border-color: transparent; padding-inline: 8px; }\n    .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--accent); }\n    .btn-arrow::after { content: '→'; transition: transform 0.15s ease; }\n    .btn-arrow:hover::after { transform: translateX(2px); }\n    .card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 28px; }\n    .card-flat { background: transparent; border: 0; padding: 0; }\n    .card-rule { background: transparent; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--fg); padding: 24px 0 0; border-radius: 0; }\n    .feature .feature-mark {\n      width: 36px; height: 36px; display: grid; place-items: center;\n      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 2px; color: var(--muted);\n      margin-bottom: var(--gap-md);\n    }\n    .feature .feature-mark svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; }\n    .feature h3 { margin-bottom: 6px; }\n    .feature p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }\n    .stat .stat-num {\n      font-family: var(--font-display);\n      font-size: clamp(56px, 8vw, 96px);\n      line-height: 0.95;\n      letter-spacing: -0.04em;\n      color: var(--fg);\n      font-weight: 500;\n    }\n    .stat .stat-label { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 8px; max-width: 24ch; }\n    .stat .stat-unit { font-size: 0.5em; opacity: 0.7; margin-left: 2px; }\n    .quote { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(26px, 2.8vw, 36px); line-height: 1.22; letter-spacing: -0.01em; max-width: 30ch; }\n    .quote-author { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: var(--gap-md); }\n    .quote-mark { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 140px; line-height: 0.7; color: var(--fg); opacity: 0.12; margin-bottom: -28px; }\n    .pill {\n      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; padding: 4px 10px;\n      background: transparent; color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: 999px; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px;\n      letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase;\n    }\n    .tag { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; padding: 4px 10px; background: transparent; color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 999px; font-size: 12px; }\n    .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }\n    .field label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }\n    .input, .textarea {\n      width: 100%; padding: 11px 14px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius);\n      background: var(--surface); color: var(--fg); font: inherit;\n    }\n    .textarea { min-height: 110px; resize: vertical; }\n    .ds-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15px; }\n    .ds-table th, .ds-table td { padding: 16px 12px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: left; vertical-align: top; }\n    .ds-table th { color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; }\n    .ds-table .num-col { text-align: right; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }\n    .ph-img {\n      background:\n        linear-gradient(135deg, color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 86%, var(--fg)) 0%, var(--surface) 55%, color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg) 84%, var(--fg)) 100%);\n      border: 1px solid var(--border);\n      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);\n      min-height: 280px;\n      display: grid; place-items: center;\n      color: var(--muted);\n      font-family: var(--font-mono);\n      font-size: 12px;\n      letter-spacing: 0.08em;\n      text-transform: uppercase;\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .wide { aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; }\n    .portrait { aspect-ratio: 4 / 5; }\n    .square { aspect-ratio: 1; }\n    .rule { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .rule-strong { border-top: 1px solid var(--fg); }\n    .log-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr 120px; gap: var(--gap-lg); padding: 22px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); align-items: start; }\n    .pull { justify-self: end; }\n    .hero-split { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr; gap: var(--gap-xl); align-items: center; }\n    .hero-center { text-align: center; max-width: 860px; margin-inline: auto; }\n    .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: var(--gap-sm); flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: flex-start; }\n    .hero-center .hero-cta { justify-content: center; }\n    @media (max-width: 920px) { .hero-split { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .log-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .pull { justify-self: start; } }\n    .hero-plate {\n      position: relative;\n      min-height: 690px;\n      display: grid;\n      align-items: end;\n      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);\n      overflow: hidden;\n    }\n    .hero-plate::before {\n      content: \"\";\n      position: absolute;\n      inset: 0;\n      background:\n        linear-gradient(90deg, var(--bg), color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg) 72%, transparent), transparent),\n        linear-gradient(0deg, var(--bg), transparent 46%),\n        url(\"assets/dining-room.jpg\") center / cover;\n      opacity: 0.92;\n    }\n    .hero-plate .container { position: relative; padding-block: 96px; }\n    .brand-mark { width: min(360px, 64vw); margin-bottom: 44px; }\n    .hero-copy { max-width: 780px; }\n    .hero-copy .lead { color: var(--fg); opacity: 0.86; }\n    .announce { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--surface); color: var(--muted); }\n    .announce .container { padding-block: 10px; display: flex; justify-content: center; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; }\n    .image-card { position: relative; min-height: 420px; background-size: cover; background-position: center; border: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .image-card::after { content: \"\"; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(0deg, color-mix(in oklch, var(--bg) 82%, transparent), transparent 58%); }\n    .image-card > * { position: relative; z-index: 1; }\n    .image-card.menu { background-image: url(\"assets/fire-table.jpg\"); }\n    .image-card.bar { background-image: url(\"assets/bar.jpg\"); }\n    .destination { min-height: 360px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end; }\n    .destination p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 0; }\n    .menu-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr 88px; gap: 20px; padding: 18px 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .menu-row h3 { font-size: 21px; }\n    .menu-row p { margin: 4px 0 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }\n    .page-links { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }\n    .page-links a { background: var(--surface); padding: 22px; min-height: 132px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }\n    .page-links a:hover { background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 88%, var(--fg)); }\n    .smallcaps { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"announce\">\n    <div class=\"container\">Complimentary validated parking at The Star when you dine with Dark Shepherd.</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"topnav\">\n    <div class=\"container topnav-inner\">\n      <a class=\"logo\" href=\"index.html\" aria-label=\"Dark Shepherd home\"><img src=\"assets/dark-shepherd-logo.png\" alt=\"Dark Shepherd\" /></a>\n      <nav class=\"row\" aria-label=\"Primary navigation\">\n        <a href=\"menu.html\">Menus</a>\n        <a href=\"functions.html\">Functions</a>\n        <a href=\"drinks-menu.html\">Drinks</a>\n        <a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a>\n      </nav>\n      <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\">Bookings</a>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <main id=\"content\">\n    <section class=\"hero-plate\" data-od-id=\"hero\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"hero-copy stack\">\n          <img class=\"brand-mark\" src=\"assets/dark-shepherd-logo.png\" alt=\"Dark Shepherd\" />\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Mediterranean restaurant · The Star Brisbane</p>\n          <h1>Born of fire. Bound by flavour.</h1>\n          <p class=\"lead\">White Pyrenees lamb, live seafood, dry-aged cuts and a Marana Forni oven set the tone for an all-day Mediterranean dining room on The Terrace.</p>\n          <div class=\"hero-cta\">\n            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\">Reserve a table</a>\n            <a class=\"btn btn-secondary\" href=\"menu.html\">View menu</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"destinations\">\n      <div class=\"container stack\" style=\"gap: 56px;\">\n        <div class=\"row-between\">\n          <div style=\"max-width: 44ch;\">\n            <p class=\"eyebrow\">Enter the room</p>\n            <h2>Fire, flavour, and flair.</h2>\n          </div>\n          <p class=\"lead\">A concept navigation system that keeps the existing site intent intact while making each path feel like part of the same ritual.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"grid-3\">\n          <article class=\"card destination image-card menu\">\n            <p class=\"smallcaps\">Menus</p>\n            <h3>Woodfire, lamb, seafood and village plates.</h3>\n            <p>Main menu, lunch specials, banquets and seasonal feasts stay one step from booking.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"card destination\">\n            <p class=\"smallcaps\">Functions</p>\n            <h3>Host boldly, dine brilliantly.</h3>\n            <p>A 120-seat dining room and semi-private 10-seater for celebrations, private dinners and events.</p>\n          </article>\n          <article class=\"card destination image-card bar\">\n            <p class=\"smallcaps\">The bar</p>\n            <h3>Shadows rise, and spirits flow.</h3>\n            <p>Signature cocktails, premium spirits, chilled biers and a curated 140-bottle wine list.</p>\n          </article>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"provenance\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-1-2\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">The flock gathers</p>\n          <h2>Lamb meets fire's embrace.</h2>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"stack\">\n          <p class=\"lead\">By night, the embers smoulder. By day, the sun casts light on Mediterranean marvels. The experience is built around provenance: White Pyrenees lamb, live seafood tanks, a dry-aging lamb cabinet and char from the Marana Forni oven.</p>\n          <div class=\"grid-3\">\n            <div class=\"stat\">\n              <div class=\"stat-num num\">7<span class=\"stat-unit\"> days</span></div>\n              <p class=\"stat-label\">all-day dining from 11am until late, except Christmas Day.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat\">\n              <div class=\"stat-num num\">120</div>\n              <p class=\"stat-label\">seat dining room for the main restaurant experience.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"stat\">\n              <div class=\"stat-num num\">140</div>\n              <p class=\"stat-label\">bottle wine list paired to bold Mediterranean flavours.</p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"menu-preview\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-2-1\">\n        <div>\n          <p class=\"eyebrow\">Menu markers</p>\n          <h2>Offerings with old URL intent preserved.</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin-top: 18px;\">The companion menu page keeps a condensed editorial view of real dishes and banquet paths, with full menu intent pointing to the existing `/menu`, `/menus`, and `/banquets` routes.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div>\n          <div class=\"menu-row\">\n            <span class=\"meta\">Snacks</span>\n            <div><h3>Woodfired Pillow Bread</h3><p>Thyme and olive oil, or feta, olives and capers.</p></div>\n            <span class=\"meta num\">$14+</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"menu-row\">\n            <span class=\"meta\">Small plates</span>\n            <div><h3>Woodfired Octopus</h3><p>Olive oil and fava.</p></div>\n            <span class=\"meta num\">$38</span>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"menu-row\">\n            <span class=\"meta\">Large plates</span>\n            <div><h3>White Pyrenees Lamb Shoulder</h3><p>Slow-cooked in the woodfired oven, served with tzatziki.</p></div>\n            <span class=\"meta num\">$60 / $120</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"functions-bar\">\n      <div class=\"container grid-2\">\n        <div class=\"card-rule stack\">\n          <p class=\"smallcaps\">Functions & events</p>\n          <h2>Carve moments into memories.</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\">Grand celebrations can take the 120-seat venue. More intimate gatherings can retreat into the semi-private 10-seater, veiled in shadow and ceremony.</p>\n          <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-arrow\" href=\"functions.html\">View functions concept</a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"card-rule stack\">\n          <p class=\"smallcaps\">The bar</p>\n          <h2>Every glass tells a tale.</h2>\n          <p class=\"lead\">Signature cocktails twist classics with precision, while the wine list and premium spirits give the restaurant a second evening rhythm.</p>\n          <a class=\"btn btn-secondary btn-arrow\" href=\"drinks-menu.html\">Explore drinks</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"site-map\">\n      <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"page-links\">\n          <a href=\"menu.html\"><span class=\"smallcaps\">Page 01</span><strong>Main menu</strong></a>\n          <a href=\"functions.html\"><span class=\"smallcaps\">Page 02</span><strong>Functions</strong></a>\n          <a href=\"drinks-menu.html\"><span class=\"smallcaps\">Page 03</span><strong>Drinks</strong></a>\n          <a href=\"contact.html\"><span class=\"smallcaps\">Page 04</span><strong>Contact</strong></a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" data-od-id=\"cta-strip\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n      <div class=\"container\" style=\"max-width: 680px;\">\n        <h2>When the embers glow.</h2>\n        <p class=\"lead\" style=\"margin: 16px auto 32px;\">All Day Dining · 7 Days · 11am-Late · The Terrace, Level 4, The Star Brisbane.</p>\n        <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://www.sevenrooms.com/explore/darkshepherd/reservations/create/search?venues=darkshepherd,pompetteau,yamasgreekdrink,stilts,richandrarerestaurant,fatcowrestaurant,longwangchopstickhouse,opabarmezze,massimorestaurantandbar,foshbarrestaurant\">Book Dark Shepherd</a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </main>\n\n  <footer class=\"pagefoot\">\n    <div class=\"container row-between\">\n      <span>Dark Shepherd · The Terrace, Level 4, The Star Brisbane · Ph. <a href=\"tel:+61721116869\">(07) 2111 6869</a></span>\n      <span><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/darkshepherd_bne/\">Instagram</a> · <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/darkshepherd.brisbane\">Facebook</a> · <a href=\"contact.html\">Contact</a></span>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n","isError":false}

